<li id="cite_note-10">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFReeves2015" class="citation book cs1">Reeves, Richard (9 February 2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=JQlYBQAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PT155"><i>John Stuart Mill: Victorian Firebrand</i></a>. Atlantic Books. p. 309. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a> <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-78239-713-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-78239-713-7"><bdi>978-1-78239-713-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=John+Stuart+Mill%3A+Victorian+Firebrand&amp;rft.pages=309&amp;rft.pub=Atlantic+Books&amp;rft.date=2015-02-09&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-78239-713-7&amp;rft.aulast=Reeves&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DJQlYBQAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPT155&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThomas+Hare+%28political+reformer%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-Crawford-11">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Crawford_11-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Crawford_11-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
